(3265, 87440, 'A Day Trip - CD1', 'Gavintoo’s Biography\r\nGavintoo, Chinese electronica/hiphop producer，best known for his beautiful melody and strange name Bai Tian Bu Liang (it means the day won’t light) among electronica & hiphop music fans in China. His music is beautiful and elegant he plant the Chinese romantic mood deep into electronica and hiphop music.\r\nA DAY TRIP is his debut LP, released by the young and fresh Chinese independent music label MINTELEC RECORDS. This double concept album contains 5 chapters: Good morning, yesterday, Floating with light, Tea time，Street of sunset and Good evening，Mr. Miss.\r\nDisc 1 contains Good morning, yesterday and Floating with light, it brings listeners trips in the morning and floating with the light, Disc 2 is made for the PM time, you will see the light of daydream mellows into the midnight. It’s a magic trip ,beautiful, warm and soft.\r\n', '2011-01-21 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, '李天皋', 'Mintelec Records', 0, '', 1, 0, '2011-03-15 19:41:39', '2015-02-16 15:47:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
